            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">ἡ βουλὴ καὶ</supplied> ὁ δῆ<lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">μος τῶν</supplied> Κορ<supplied reason="lost">ιν</supplied>θίων <lb n="3"/>μη<supplied reason="lost">νι</supplied>είων <supplied reason="lost">σί</supplied>των <lb n="4"/>ἕνε<supplied reason="lost">κ</supplied>εν καὶ ἐπὶ τ<supplied reason="lost">ῆς πάσης εὐν</supplied>οίας <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>εντεπαιλ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>λ<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>ωπο<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> πα</supplied>ρέσχησ<supplied reason="lost">εν</supplied> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>υ ἀρετῆ<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>σωποκιλο<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift besteht aus drei Fragmenten. Die Maße des Fr. b sind: Höhe: -32.5; Breite: -12.6; Tiefe: 5.2. Die Maße des Fr. c sind: Höhe: -37; Breite: -18.5; Tiefe: 6.7.</p>
